title: Pettiny 20 XL Cat Litter Tray Liners with Drawstrings Scratch Resistant Bags for Extra Large Litter Box
features: 20 EXTRA LARGE LITTER TRAY LINERS — Pack of 20 individually folded XL cat tray liners of 97 cm x 43 cm. Ideal for jumbo litter trays up to 60 cm x 48 cm and perfect for multi-cat households. Our eco-friendly cat litter liners are partially made using recycled materials.

EXTRA STRONG MATERIAL — Unlike other brands, Pettiny liners are made using a special polymer density blend for extra toughness. Our heavy-duty litter box bags are scratch, rip and tear resistant and strong enough to withstand even the most determined scratching.

QUICK, EASY AND HYGIENIC — With easy to use drawstrings, you can quickly clean your kitty's litter box with no spillage. Cleaning your cat's litter tray has never been easier; simply pull the drawstrings, tie shut and toss away. Keep your cat's litter pan and surrounding area always clean.

LEAKPROOF BAGS — Our exceptionally thick litter box liners prevent urine and unpleasant odours from sticking to your litter pan, extending the life of your tray. There is no scrubbing, no sticking and no mess. Enjoy a hassle-free cleanup.

PERFECT FIT — No matter what type of litter box your kitty prefers, our adaptable cat tray liners can be used in covered or open litter boxes and are designed to be comfortably fitted into corner or odd shaped trays.
description: Product Description Scratch and Tear Resistant Thick and strong liners that will resist even the most playful cats and will not rip when it's time to clean up. Strong Polymer Formula Our exclusive formula combines the high density polymers and tear resistance properties of low density polymers, helping us stand out from the rest. Easy to use Drawstrings Enjoy a smooth cleanup with our handy and strong drawstrings that won't snap when it's time to dispose. Quick and Hygienic Keep your hands clean and your litter tray fresh with our leakproof bags that prevent urine and unpleasant odors from sticking to your litter trays. Don't Settle For Less Pettiny Leakproof Cat Litter Tray Liners Pettiny liners are made from a unique polymer density mix that combines the toughness of high density polymers with the rip and tear resistance of low density polymers, bringing you the best of both worlds. Our exceptionally thick litter tray liners prevent urine and unpleasant odors from sticking to your litter pan, extending the life of your litter trays.
